('en','elettronica','Electronics','Technical consulting and support for devices and components.','We support industrial companies in selecting, diagnosing and integrating electronic devices, components and custom solutions.','["Electronics consulting","Industrial devices","Components","Diagnostics","Technical support"]',2),
('en','sicurezza','Security','Physical and digital protection for your company.','We integrate video surveillance, access control, alarm systems, cybersecurity, backup and data protection.','["Video surveillance","Access control","Alarm systems","Cybersecurity","Backup and data protection"]',3),
('en','automazione','Automation','Smart systems for more efficient processes.','We build industrial automation, device integration, process control and intelligent data-connected systems.','["Industrial automation","Device integration","Process control","Smart systems"]',4),
