('en','energia-green','Green energy','Sustainable technology for energy production and monitoring.','We support photovoltaic projects with batteries, inverters, consumption monitoring and sustainable energy solutions.','["Photovoltaic","Batteries","Inverters","Consumption monitoring","Sustainable energy"]',6),
